Text:
@chabak (and others): the torrent has two trackers listed. One is for smartorrent, and the other is piratebay. I do not know about transmission, but in uTorrent, if you right-click on the torrent, select "properties", it will show which trackers are used. In uTorrent, there was not the necessary empty line required between trackers (so they show as separate trackers).

You can either insert the line, or delete the smartorrent tracker (since it really isn't a valid tracker.

HTH
